title: Coding Workshop
details: This is a night dedicated to playing with and discussing the data visualization tool D3.js. Come by to hear presentations from fellow coders. Anyone is welcome to be an audience member -- reach out to me if there's a topic you'd like to hear about or present on!

title: Coding Social
details: Coding social for anyone in Bloomington-Normal and beyond. Come hang out, talk about your passions, and talk trash about Objective-C (if you wish). I doubled checked to make sure there wasn't trivia on this night. Bring ideas for what you'd like to get out of this group - whether it be demos, workshops, questions, personal projects, networking, school, general interest, or what have you
